content: On the evening of May 28, outside the Taipei Legislative Yuan, people worked together to send a giant balloon with the words "Reject China's Interference" into the Legislative Yuan.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Supplement: A survey on college students' mental health published in the journal Frontiers in Psychology in August 2021, led by the Peking University Huilongguan Clinical School, Chengde Medical College, and Beijing Anding Hospital affiliated to Capital Medical University, showed that during the COVID-19 pandemic, 37% of the subjects experienced symptoms of depression, about 25% of the subjects experienced symptoms of anxiety, and 7.3% of the subjects had suicidal thoughts. Women are more likely to be depressed than men, but men are less likely to be depressed.

content: In addition, Phnom Penh also built a Mao Zedong Avenue in 1965.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: People's Daily reported on May 28 that Xi Jinping asked at a symposium between enterprises and experts: "What is the main reason for the decline in the number of new unicorn companies?"

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: In the early morning of May 28-29, Guang'an, Sichuan. The owners of Chengping Shengshi Community protested outside the community due to parking issues. During the protest, some owners and police officers had disputes and pushed each other.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On May 24, Wenchang, Hainan Province, issued the "Implementation Plan for the Standardization of Non-Staff Employment in Wenchang Municipal Government Agencies and Institutions", which will clean up non-staff employment in government agencies and institutions across the city. The number of non-staff personnel in each agency shall not exceed 10% of the current establishment.
The plan also clearly states that non-staff personnel with a college degree or below (a high school degree or below for auxiliary police officers) will be cleaned up in each unit, and non-staff employees in primary and secondary schools in the education system will be cleaned up and standardized.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On May 27, Pingdingshan, Henan. A teacher posted on a social platform that Pingdingshan No. 1 Middle School New District Senior High School 1 has been in arrears of social insurance for teachers for two years, and wages have not been paid since March. Even the salaries of restaurant and security guards have been in arrears. 
As a result, someone in the comment area accused her of "not bringing bad things to the unit during her tenure, which is the most basic professional quality. If she doesn't want to work anymore, she can resign."

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:

Actually, no one seemed to dare to give an answer at yesterday's symposium.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
May 28, Shanghai. The boss of Jimu Galaxy Digital Technology Co., Ltd. was reported to have run away, and nearly a thousand people were unemployed. According to internal employees, the company's boss has lost contact, and nearly a thousand employees have not received their wages for several months, with a cumulative loss of up to 6.2 billion yuan.
Public information shows that Shanghai Jimu Galaxy Digital Technology Co., Ltd. was established in February 2023 with a registered capital of 78.61 million yuan. The legal representative is Chen Qun. It is a company engaged in software development and other related fields.

content:
Recently, many places have responded and lowered mortgage interest rates.
According to the Shanghai Securities News, more than ten provinces have followed suit, canceling the lower limit of mortgage interest rates and lowering the down payment ratio.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Recently, at the 7th Asian Drama School Student Drama Exhibition hosted by the Central Academy of Drama, Japan's Toho Gakuin's "The Goat and the Boy Walking into the Cave" was accused of mourning the Japanese soldiers who died in World War II, sparking dissatisfaction and boycott from the majority of netizens.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
University Hengshui
Recently, after the new president of the Chengdu campus of Southwest Petroleum University took office, he severely exploited students' rest time. Originally, freshmen had to attend evening self-study, but now sophomores and juniors have to attend evening self-study. And the students' winter and summer vacations were compressed. Many students expressed dissatisfaction on social media, but these comments were deleted on a large scale on various platforms.
At the same time, the school issued a notice asking students not to participate in any discussion

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 29, a young man in a Shanghai park was questioned by a security guard while reciting foreign poetry: "Is there no poetry in China's 5,000 years of culture? Why don't you spread China's positive energy?"

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 29, at the routine press conference of the Taiwan Affairs Office of the State Council, the spokesperson once again emphasized that Taiwanese artists' reposts of statements supporting unification "are all natural and true expressions of their feelings."

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
May 28, Linxia, Gansu. Villagers questioned whether there was shoddy work in the post-earthquake reconstruction project in Dahejia Town, Jishishan County.
Villagers said that the cement in some resettlement sites would break if pressed, and some had no steel bars.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 28, in Jinan, Shandong, a woman posted a video to report the director of Shuangshan No. 1 Police Station in Zhangqiu District under her real name.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: From May 27 to 28, more than 100 migrant workers in Zhengzhou Airport Economic Zone went to the Urban Investment Company to demand their wages. According to insiders, the money for BYD's road construction project was misappropriated by the Urban Investment Company to pay wages to other units.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Some netizens have found out that as early as 2021, one of the victims of the Tongling building collapse accident wrote a letter to the Party Secretary of Datong Town, pointing out that the house was in a state of disrepair due to shoddy workmanship and cracks on the roof.
At that time, Secretary Ma replied that he would apply for a renovation project for the community and would immediately organize its implementation after approval.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On May 28 (the date the video was leaked), in front of Tiananmen Square on Chang'an Avenue in Beijing, the video shows a taxi crashing into the guardrail. The vehicle was severely damaged, and a suspected policeman was knocked to the ground. Several policemen were breaking the windows of the taxi.
